description: Just under 1,000 Covid vaccinations have arrived in the island.
title: Covid vaccine: Guernsey receives Pfizer/BioNTech
title_page: Covid vaccine: Guernsey receives Pfizer/BioNTech - BBC News
maintext: Dr Brink said a further delivery of 975 doses was expected next week, but as two doses are required they would have to ensure a second dose of the same vaccine is available for those who have received their first dose.
